SIF TEQUIP:PLAYER:콘돔 || TCVAR:ARG:피임약
	RETURNF 0
SIF TALENT:ARG:유치 && !TALENT:ARG:초경
	RETURNF 0
SIF TALENT:ARG:비생물 || TALENT:ARG:봉래인 || TALENT:ARG:임신
	RETURNF 0
